    "Both of these challenges are well-suited for LLMs, as the quality of the initial systems is sufficient to utilize context and rectify mistakes reliably.",
    "This system paper presented KIT's submission for the offline track in the constrained + LLMs condition, focusing on the English-to-German translation direction.",
